cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MA, cs.SY, cs.RO 

The paper involves the use of reinforcement learning and multi-agent systems to optimize traffic flow across multiple intersections. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves the use of deep learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The use of multiple agents and coordination among them suggests the category cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems). The paper also involves the use of control theory to optimize traffic flow, which makes cs.SY (Systems and Control) a possible category. Finally, the paper involves the use of robotics to implement the AI agent, which makes cs.RO (Robotics) a possible category as well.
